{{Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Magic| name=Pygmy Puff| type=Creature| features=Small, fluffy, brightly colored| appearance=[[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Books/Half-Blood Prince|''Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince'']]}}
== Overview ==
{{Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Beginner Spoiler}}
A '''''Pygmy Puff''''' is a miniature [[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Magic/Puffskein|Puffskein]].
== Analysis ==
We are introduced to Pygmy Puffs in [[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Books/Half-Blood Prince|''Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince'']] when [[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Characters/Ginny Weasley|Ginny Weasley]] buys one from [[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Places/Weasleys' Wizard Wheezes|Weasleys' Wizard Wheezes]]. They are pink and purple miniature Puffskeins and, according to [[Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Characters/Fred and George Weasley|Fred and George]], are very popular.
== Questions == {{Muggles' Guide to Harry Potter/Questions}}
